reviews.text: Great hotel. Wouldn't quite give it a full 5-star rating, but very close. If the gym were bigger; hotel room shower/tub had more space..small things. Overall, my stay was great and it was a good bargain. Short walking distance to Starbucks, restaurants and train. I recommend taking train to Central & Mongkok stations for self-walking tour of this grand city!

Very spacious hotel with a grand staircase perfect for a reception. The dining area has a lot of echo as the furnishings are hard and modern. The food is fine. The pool is on the 3rd floor and agreeable. Unfortunately a new freeway and another hotel were being built nearby in 2016.

Great location and facilities. Metro station is walkable. Has stunning views of Harbor area. McDonald's walkable distance. Serves Indian food in buffet.
Breakfast spread is good

Wonderful view and clean room. Musician playing at the lobby created pleasant mood but no pictures  allowed. I found it rude because  she was playing in a public area for the hotel guests. 
Le 188 roof top was a great choice. Average spending for one is 500 hk$

The hotel is exquisite, and the location is great! 
The service were excellent! I really recommend club deluxe/club premier, then you get access to breakfast in the roof restaurant. It was outstanding!

reviews.text: 棒👍
とてもきれいなホテルでした。部屋は広く、窓から眺める外の景色もとても美しくよい立地だと思います。MTR炮台山駅から歩いてすぐの場所で、近くにコンビニやスタバなどもありとても便利です。MTRを利用すれば中環や湾仔などへの移動も便利です。
早餐選擇豐富，有自助餐跟單點可以任選，入住貴賓樓層服務很棒，每天都會有迎賓水果，客戶生日當天早上餐廳服務人員還會送上蛋糕，出外旅遊晚上回房後還看到送上一瓶紅酒，感覺到飯店人員的服務真的很貼心，以客為尊，下次還會想再入住港島海逸君綽酒店。
以香港的物價來說，這飯店算CP還不錯，只是人員的服務素質待加強，真的沒親切感，可能是香港人普遍都這樣吧

reviews.text: Highly recommend this restaurant for dinner.  Beautiful decor, delicious food, great seaview, nice ambience and fantastic service. Yet the price is quite reasonable. The location is convenient. Just an awesome place to dine.
君綽軒：服務周到，味道可以，部份桌子有海景。
不錯的中菜餐館，但切餅費竟然要收200元，是否有些過份!
地方及服務都良好、因今天主要跟朋友談業務、未能對美食品嘗、下次一定會再走訪
